{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop taxing Longer Separation Allowance on British armed forces",
        "additional_details": "LSA also helps ease the emotional, personal, and financial strain these separations place on soldiers and their loved ones.",
        "background": "We want the Government to stop taxing Longer Separation Allowance (LSA) which compensates British service personnel for unavoidable extended time away from their families due to deployments and training.  ",
